title: Large junior 1 bedroom,  corner unit
posting_body: ['Nice studio, comfortable space:', '*   corner unit.', 'windows on 3 sides (living area, sleeping area, kitchen)', '*   Walled off sleeping room for added privacy', '*   large size, over 550 sq feet', '*   separate kitchen and full bath', '*   elevator building (2nd floor of 7 story building)', '*   super on site', '*   walking distance to the United Nations, NYU hospitals, Grand Central', '1 year lease.', ' co-op requires complete application process that takes about 6 weeks.', '(Please make sure you allow for the wait time.)', ' Application requires written references, bank statement, tax return.', 'Quiet neighborhood.', 'Safe street.', 'across from St. Vartan park.', 'heat, water included.', 'tenant pays for phone, internet, electricity and cooking gas.', 'non-smoking building.', 'no pet.', 'serious inquiry only.']
